            "worstRating": "1"
          },
          "reviewBody": "This is a commercial institution more than a school. Bullying is not just overlooked but encouraged by the school administration. The only school where teachers themselves go through bullying while advicing the kids who go through bully to be resilient and strong towards bullying rather than addressing the wrong doer. The teachers proudly say that they can give counselling to the student who undergoes bullying from the way they learnt how they encountered the same from the bully they are facing in the school. Kavita Saraf is one classic example for arrogance. She addresses a problem by calculation of money. She cant compromise money for a single child's welfare. If u want to send your child to a school only for fame you can choose this school. If discipline and character matter, better pause and reconsider. Students will go to any extent but teachers will be sitting blind folded, lips zipped and with deaf ears. Because thats how they have been instructed. They have zero tolerence towards bullying well drafted only on papers. Your mails will never be responded. Your concerns will never be addressed. Once your child is enrolled, your child becomes either a victim or a wrongdoer. I had to change my child's school in the midway as the school turned deafears towards my complaint against bullying in the class. worst ever school.",
